title: Icona Breakfast Collection by De'Longhi (2012)
description:
The De’Longhi Icona Collection is a suite of stylish kitchen essentials that evokes the essence of 1950's la dolce vita.
The collection adds a touch of class, creativity and elegance to any kitchen. For more information please visit the links below:

DE'LONGHI OFFICIAL YOUTUBE CHANNELS -

Official De'Longhi How-To channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/delonghihowtouk
